@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cqtlvb(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.sin(tmp)
    v0 = (v0 - (wp.exp(v1 + 0.42) - v0))
    tmp = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.45 - tmp + 0.24)) - (wp.abs(tmp + 0.86) / 0.90))
    tmp = v0
    data[tid] = v0
